data.description: Welcome home to this 2 family that includes a finished basement! This is a great house for an owner occupant or the savvy investor. The first floor is a recently renovated and spacious 2 bedroom apartment with direct access to the backyard. The second floor is a cozier 2 bedroom unit that is also recently renovated. The basement provides additional living space, a full bathroom and a separate entrance. Other upgrades include a new roof and tankless water heater for an endless supply of hot water. Schedule your private tour today!
